"Neko Big Plushie"... I wonder if that's the official name?

349
00:32:07,143 --> 00:32:12,093
わぁー！なんと作ることになりました！イエーイ！
Whoa! We're actually making them! Yay!

350
00:32:12,143 --> 00:32:18,093
